-- MOVES-BlueBay hires ex-citi executive Groenenberg for macro fund
-- By Nishant Kumar
-- Tue Sep 16, 2014 04:16AM EDT
-- None



LONDON, Sept 16 (Reuters) - BlueBay Asset Management has hired the former head of emerging markets strategy at Citi <C.N>, Wike Groenenberg, for a new role as alternatives strategy director for its macro fund.

Groenenberg, who will also oversee the fund's investor relations, was responsible for generating trade ideas and marketing them to investors at the Wall Street bank in London.